extends layout

block content
  include _header

  h3 Preview
  i Note: This will be a context based preview. Videos will show a random frame, picture will just be picture itself, document will be just the first paragraph, music will have an mp3 player for a listening preview, unsupported file types will not have any previews.

  h3 Summary
  p #{file.summary}

  br

  h3 Tags
  for kw in file.keywords
    p= kw

  br

  a.button-negative Delete File